{"tid":1789832,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"「政、法」二者誰先行？ - 李碧華","createTime":"2019-12-19T14:23:22.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-19T15:10:52.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"114102341922e7b1b06a778ee56afb60082487dc","tid":1789832,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-19T14:23:22.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/columnist/%E6%9D%8E%E7%A2%A7%E8%8F%AF/daily/article/20191219/20827403/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Fcolumnist%2F%25E6%259D%258E%25E7%25A2%25A7%25E8%258F%25AF%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20191219%2F20827403%2F&d=d86Hk5Pgd4X%2FjIl3nTqvfBjE8xiivR5AeW87zNloLfY%3D&h=669b11e9\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Fcolumnist%2F%25E6%259D%258E%25E7%25A2%25A7%25E8%258F%25AF%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20191219%2F20827403%2F&h=fc13ffce\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/columnist/%E6%9D%8E%E7%A2%A7%E8%8F%AF/daily/article/20191219/20827403/</a><br />\n<br />\n「政、法」二者誰先行？ - 李碧華<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple_sub/20191219/large/1576660387_b9af.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple_sub%2F20191219%2Flarge%2F1576660387_b9af.jpg&h=6deb5210&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nContinue Hong Kong Limited fb圖片(互聯網)<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n有俗語謎面：「拍馬屁拍到馬腿上」，打一成語，謎底是「眼高手低」。「拍馬屁拍到馬春袋」則更糟，是「前後不分」或「一失手成千古恨」──拍歪了拍錯了，是「反效果」，甚至令人恥笑。<br />\n<br />\n何妖上位以來，言行品格及嘴臉都令人側目，而自721與元朗白衣黑幫握手示好之後，一直冇運行，失了一樣又一樣，連人帶馬所有相關榮譽一場空，不知其母校皇仁書院舊生會有超過83%意向能否終止何妖會籍？英國安格里亞魯斯金大學調查過其操守後，已撤銷2011年授予的榮譽法學博士學位了。<br />\n<br />\n才一個月，跌落地揦返拃沙，何妖獲中國政法大學頒「法學名譽博士」學位。與當年新界王劉皇發涉嫌「買賣」所得相同，該校一級教授方流芳亦非議，直言「名譽博士和學術沒有什麼關係，並非學歷。」──看來只屬「政治慰安獎」。<br />\n<br />\n唯有當事人最high。世上也有些拍馬屁群組，與「熱烈祝賀榮獲中國法政大學名譽博士學位」的何大合照──慢着，法政大學是日本東京千代田區的私立大學，人家以「法」先行，而中國的政法大學，「政」騎住「法」，所謂法，多委屈。<br />\n<br />\n也許日後會出現「律地大學」──無法無天。 <br />\n<br />\n李碧華<br />\n電郵 :mcwriter@appledaily.com"},{"pid":"07882ace2f1175a7430063f1a19a9e9914e6dae3","tid":1789832,"uid":88940,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-19T14:23:49.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://t.me/xmasevehk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fxmasevehk&d=d86Hk5Pgd4X%2FjIl3nTqvfBjE8xiivR5AeW87zNloLfY%3D&h=4af4a9a0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/xmasevehk</a><br />\n唔好意思借位<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">經濟攬炒！香港人果七千萬比人搞啊！佢老母仲OT成九億<br />\n1221<br />\n1224<br />\n1225<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><br />\n1224！［行動宜家唔推幾時推？］平安夜 賀佢老母呀！</span><br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1789301\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1789301</a>"},{"pid":"4fde0d2f58db404df16dc4f3ce65124792be7a2b","tid":1789832,"uid":191271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-19T14:24:11.000Z","msg":"【致英國及美國政府的公開信】 《中英聯合聲明》- 條約簽署之第35年<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1789766\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1789766</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"e39f4885938aa46f4df22907d65f365455023bf0","tid":1789832,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-19T14:24:17.000Z","msg":"20 DEC 2019 星期五 <br />\n全民口罩日<br />\n<br />\n日期:20/12/2019(五)<br />\n時間：8:00pm開始<br />\n【和你撐手足】荔枝角聲援手足集會<br />\n地點：荔枝角收押所外（九龍蝴蝶谷道5號）<br />\n⭐️已批不反對通知書<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n日期:2019年12月21日(星期六)<br />\n時間:下午1時至5時<br />\n杜絕政治酬庸<br />\n銀髮族集會<br />\n地點:愛丁堡廣場大會堂對出空地<br />\n不反對通知書申請中<br />\nfacebook銀髮族老而不廢<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n12.21 元朗見<br />\nSat 15:00 YOHO MALL<br />\n毋忘721恐襲<br />\nRemembering 721 Terror<br />\n<br />\n通告 Notice<br />\n如元朗党鉄站提早至下午關閉,<br />\n活動將於下列商場繼續:<br />\n屯門   V city<br />\n沙田  連城廣場<br />\n荃灣  荃灣廣場<br />\n將軍澳 Popcorn<br />\n中環  ifc mall<br />\n元朗 YOНО MALL"},{"pid":"069f510befb65779e382f0b7a72b8d9a709b61a7","tid":178